', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/110551/', '[1] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[2] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0', 1767365206);
